description: Gobble brings home cookin' on the road!  Favorite Comforts:  Pulled BBQ Sandwiches, Pot Pies & Shepherd's Pie, Bacon-Wrapped Mac 'n Cheese on a Stick, Roast Turkey with all the Fixings, Smoked Turkey Legs, Hot Wings, Chili, Meat Pasties (pies), and daily specials inspired by season or flavor.  We feature hot and cold sandwiches & wraps with hand-carved meats and signature meat salads, and Salads.  Sides include fries & gravy, secret recipe mashed potatoes, corn muffin, slaws & salads.  Save room for dessert!  Chewy brownies, pumpkin cheesecake, apple tarts, fresh baked cookies, with seasonal specials.Gobble also offers take-home meals in microwave/oven save containers.  We also catering all size events, from a family reunion to huge Corporate Meetings, with a menu customized for you.
name: Gobble Comfort Food
